Interface RequestParser<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The request type
    All Superinterfaces:
    Initializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CommandLineArgumentsParser, HTTPRequestParser, MailMessageParser
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRequestParser, DefaultCommandLineArgumentsParser, DefaultMailMessageParser, MultiPartHTTPRequestParser, SimpleHTTPRequestParser

    public interface RequestParser<T>
extends Initializable
    This interface defines the fax bridge request parser used to extract the fax job and file info from the input data.
    Since:
    0.41.3
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
